 Mama Routine.\n\nThese are the small, predictable tasks that:\u2028\u2714\ufe0f keep your home functioning\u2028\u2714\ufe0f prevent buildup\u2028\u2714\ufe0f remove daily guesswork\u2028\u2714\ufe0f help you stay consistent\n\u2028Just a simple rhythm.\nPrint it.\u2028Save it.\u2028Put it somewhere visible.\n\nFollow it for one week and notice how much lighter it feels when the decisions are already made.\n\nComment JULY and I\u2019ll send you the free calendar & how to follow it.", "timestamp": "2026-07-01T19:53:18.000Z", "videoDuration": 10.216, "videoPlayCount": 21844, "videoViewCount": 5893, "likesCount": 176, "commentsCount": 732, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/731950052_18604799167038124_5443094728677842331_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH_8C_fd5YRsAG6kvhdY56fs-fGqCb0eW_060zmqcDEVilsSHQgNaHTWx2EWfdY5Ow&_nc_ohc=L21jaEl2k-8Q7kNvwGZ7ORS&_nc_gid=jn5Efzu-LgB4Tx4uQCe6YA&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDMuKdGrgItdJHvx-c01LCz-qLRjR4M2zBN7aTiOK2eyg&oe=6A61E04A&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQNc2Se8g6Ao-MqoBtvBPnXtjxhf5NKnq0IzsyLYgJJdgxTqZ6xGaMwHUjo7eD1USA1_4zuPkAxFx6J4hsLJtqCdnkUp4Z0QUkDUExc.mp4?_nc_cat=106&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=doGyW5-UJxUQ7kNvwHv5HzD&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6Mjc2NDcxNDU1MDgyNDgxMDcsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjoxNywidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjEwLCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=f0776a41e7d9dfc5&_nc_&_nc_gid=V69ahMBTpRJqyxTwEVhJ2w&_nc_ss=7ca8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQA4epk-x8BgXeUelAZcBcu-XpZ_OprwOzcMRNnQTK3mQw&oe=6A5DD387", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "andreavanzo_composer", "song_name": "Soulmate x Am\u00e9lie x Interstellar x Passacaglia", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_i